-I wonder.

00:02:59.905 --> 00:03:01.705
Allow me to start the bid.

00:03:01.785 --> 00:03:03.665
My starting price is 100 liang.

00:03:05.985 --> 00:03:06.825
200 liang.

00:03:07.785 --> 00:03:09.505
How can we bid when we don't know
what it is?

00:03:11.345 --> 00:03:12.345
400 liang.

00:03:13.025 --> 00:03:14.745
400 liang already? This soon?

00:03:14.825 --> 00:03:17.625
Mr. Niu offers 400 liang.

00:03:17.705 --> 00:03:19.305
Do I hear a higher bid?

00:03:25.865 --> 00:03:26.745
3,000 liang.

00:03:28.585 --> 00:03:30.145
-3,000?
-3,000?

00:03:33.465 --> 00:03:34.505
Are you out of your mind?

00:03:34.585 --> 00:03:36.225
How generous of this gentleman.

00:03:36.305 --> 00:03:37.465
3,000 liang.

00:03:37.545 --> 00:03:39.825
