00:04:15.505 --> 00:04:16.865
Did you hear me?

00:04:25.705 --> 00:04:27.065
Two fluorite night pearls.

00:04:30.985 --> 00:04:33.105
Two fluorite night pearls.

00:04:33.185 --> 00:04:34.185
Fluorite night pearls.

00:04:39.505 --> 00:04:41.345
What an elucidating experience.

00:04:42.745 --> 00:04:44.425
That spoiled brat.

00:04:51.745 --> 00:04:53.985
What exquisite fluorite night pearls.
Fine tributes from the Western Sea.

00:04:54.065 --> 00:04:56.945
May I know where you hail from, Mr. Bai?

00:04:57.025 --> 00:04:58.465
This is just a transaction.

00:04:58.545 --> 00:05:00.785
Outside of this pleasure boat,
we're both strangers.

00:05:01.425 --> 00:05:03.545
Right. I agree.

00:05:05.625 --> 00:05:07.425
I wonder what it is
that my husband spent a fortune

00:05:07.505 --> 00:05:08.385
to purchase.

00:05:08.465 --> 00:05:09.785
When can we get it?

00:05:09.865 --> 00:05:12.225
You're so impatient, Miss. Come with me.

00:05:13.265 --> 00:05:14.105
After you.

00:05:14.625 --> 00:05:15.705
Wait for me here.

00:05:15.785 --> 00:05:17.425
I'd like to see a friend.

00:05:17.505 --> 00:05:19.225
