00:05:35.105 --> 00:05:36.145
You're alone.

00:05:39.985 --> 00:05:41.345
Oh, my dear brother. Are you worried

00:05:41.425 --> 00:05:42.265
that I might feel lonely,

00:05:42.345 --> 00:05:44.465
so you came to have
a heart-to-heart talk with me?

00:05:44.545 --> 00:05:46.025
