I say I have nothing to do with it?

00:06:12.465 --> 00:06:14.345
Whether it's your or your mother's doing,

00:06:14.945 --> 00:06:16.345
it makes no difference.

00:06:24.625 --> 00:06:25.465
Right.

00:06:28.305 --> 00:06:30.585
You lured me to Botang Pleasure Boat.

00:06:32.185 --> 00:06:33.745
What if I kill you right now?

00:06:36.345 --> 00:06:37.625
Can you kill me though?

00:06:37.705 --> 00:06:39.145
I can try.

00:06:41.545 --> 00:06:42.985
I don't have time for a spar right now.

00:06:43.625 --> 00:06:46.585
Many kids on this boat are waiting
to be rescued.

00:06:47.265 --> 00:06:48.985
Drop your act.

00:06:49.065 --> 00:06:52.185
You forsook moral
principles for the throne.

00:06:52.265 --> 00:06:54.425
A human life is nothing in your eyes,

00:06:54.945 --> 00:06:56.465
