00:07:29.865 --> 00:07:31.065
I…

00:07:33.785 --> 00:07:34.985
We have to pick the goods.

00:08:10.945 --> 00:08:12.945
They are here. Help yourself.

00:08:14.825 --> 00:08:16.665
Are these murder thralls?

00:08:17.345 --> 00:08:19.305
