00:08:25.585 --> 00:08:27.425
It's hard to make one,

00:08:27.505 --> 00:08:29.465
and that's why it's expensive.

00:08:30.705 --> 00:08:32.425
We only have 10 minutes to save them.

00:08:32.505 --> 00:08:33.745
