00:09:20.465 --> 00:09:21.305
Run!

00:09:27.745 --> 00:09:29.305
-Here.
-Mother!

00:09:29.385 --> 00:09:30.225
Careful.

00:09:30.305 --> 00:09:31.505
Careful.

00:09:41.785 --> 00:09:42.625
Here.

00:09:46.585 --> 00:09:47.425
