got the short end of the stick.

00:12:45.665 --> 00:12:48.025
His back is seriously wounded,
and he is suffering from nightmares.

00:12:48.785 --> 00:12:50.665
We don't know when he'll wake up.

00:12:55.825 --> 00:12:57.945
Bai. I'm sorry.

00:12:58.705 --> 00:13:00.025
Please be all right.

00:13:00.825 --> 00:13:01.905
What a joke.

00:13:01.985 --> 00:13:02.945
What a joke.

00:13:03.025 --> 00:13:04.985
You want to regain your power?

00:13:05.065 --> 00:13:06.465
Have you forgotten

00:13:06.545 --> 00:13:09.025
that you gave it to
us willingly in the past?

00:13:13.665 --> 00:13:14.945
Your Highness.

00:13:19.305 --> 00:13:20.705
It is cold out here,

00:13:20.785 --> 00:13:22.825
and you have a weak constitution.

00:13:22.905 --> 00:13:25.665
Why are you standing here alone?

00:13:31.865 --> 00:13:34.065
Don't do this, Your Highness.

00:13:34.145 --> 00:13:34.985
Come.

00:13:39.785 --> 00:13:40.625
